📊 Sales Performance Dashboard (Excel)
An interactive Sales Performance Dashboard built in Microsoft Excel to analyze and visualize business sales data across regions, products, customers, and time periods.

This dashboard provides clear KPI tracking and dynamic filtering to support data-driven decision making.

🚀 Project Overview
This Excel dashboard helps stakeholders:

Monitor overall sales performance
Track monthly and weekly sales trends
Compare regional sales performance
Identify top customers
Analyze product-level sales distribution
View key performance metrics at a glance

The dashboard is fully interactive using slicers for region and month selection.

